description: Emotions run high on the Bravest Warriors' ship when Danny contracts Zgraxxis fever and Wallow must perform surgery. Meanwhile, a mysterious old man has appeared, distracting everyone from the task at hand. Chris must contain his anger and save Danny, or else put all of his friends in mortal peril. Also, Beth has a tail.
name: Emotion Lord

description: Dark abomination of the Wet Mounds of Nardacorn, Chris is taking his sweet time in the bathroom! As Chris, Wallow, and Danny hog the Holo-John with their fantasies, they prevent a certain member of the Bravest Warriors team from getting a fresh start to her day.
name: Butter Lettuce

description: These are the facts: the Bravest Warriors are on a bus. Their destination: somewhere. Their goal: ... something. Wait, who are the Bravest Warriors, anyway? The team must remember their identities before they crash into the NeoMars Convention Center. Things looks pretty grim for the Bravest Whoevers, but at least they have plenty of bread.
name: Memory Donk

description: The fate of the planet Bunless 9 depends on the Bravest Warriors overcoming their adolescent fears of intimacy in order to prevent an apocalypse. Will love prevail through time, space, and fleshy buttocks?
name: The Bunless

description:
The mid-season finale of Bravest Warriors Season 1.

In a shocking encounter, the Emotion Lord returns to help the Bravest Warriors in destroying the firebugs' hive. That is, if he doesn't get them killed first. Chris learns about fate, the future, and the importance of vitamin B-12. Remember to take your vitamins, kids
name: Lavarinth

description: After a relaxing day by the lake, the Bravest Warriors meet an extraordinary—and attractive—new friend. As the boys vie for her attention, Impossibear finds a mysterious stick that sprouts unforeseen consequences from Chris's forehead. Chris discovers that with great power, comes great responsibility—and lots of emotion.
name: Gas-Powered Stick

description: The hour has come at last! Danny has constructed a time machine so he can finally seek revenge on the Low Gravity Hacker Pack who never let him join in any of their hacker games. He reveals the truth behind his dark, disgusting past, while the team learns that revenge is a meal best served cold... and kinda barfy.
name: Dan Before Time

description: In the early morning hours Chris and Danny fly from the Bravest Warriors Invisible Hideout on a mission of the utmost importance... to buy cereal for Beth. Chris must comfort a Martian chef with daddy issues and return to his best friend for their jinx-iversary.
name: Cereal Master

description: Breaking the laws of physics, Wankershim has left the Holo-John and is now taking up residence in NeoMars Park... and he's growing at an exponential rate. Meanwhile, an old friend returns to share with Chris a vision of the future, and to tell the Bravest Warriors that it's ALWAYS been Wankershim
name: Ultra Wankershim

description: When the Bravest Warriors receive mysterious gifts from the See-Through Zone, they must use their wits to unlock the door to the greatest secret. In this season finale, there promises to be more emotion, Catbug, and delicious peanut butter squares than ever before.
name: Catbug

description: When the adorable Sugarbelly aliens ask the the Bravest Warriors for help, the young heroes split up to tackle their most challenging mission yet in this cross-planetary adventure
name: Sugarbellies

description: Beth goes behind the door into the See-Through Zone to discover the mystery behind the secret message, "Ralph Waldo Pickle Chips" Everything gets epic in the Season 2 premiere of Bravest Warriors!
name: Aeon Worm

description: In this episode, Danny gets a new #1 pal and it just so happens that he looks exactly like Chris. Does this create jealousy between the bathroom bros? Find out in... RoboChris!
name: RoboChris

description: Plum returns to Bravest Warriors in this hilariously action packed adventure at an alien rescue. Danny and Plum team up to help out the adorable little aliens and Catbug is wearing a grass skirt?!
name: Mexican Touchdown

description: Ralph Waldo Pickle Chips RETURNS! Not only that but Plum and Chris are kissing, Danny has weird eyes and Wallow is drinking his ol' beer! What the heck is up with the Warriors and what does it all mean?
name: Hamster Priest

description: Jelly Kid DIES?! Who did it? Was it Wallow? Chris Kirkman the Emotion Lord? There's no way Danny did it!
name: Jelly Kid Forever

description: The horror... THE HORROR! The Warriors are stranded on a yellow planet and one by one they are... disappearing. Written by Invader Zim creator, Jhonen Vasquez, this episode is downright spooky. Featuring the guest voice talent of Dana Snyder (Master Shake from Aqua Teen Hunger Force) this is one episode you do not want to miss!
name: The Puppetyville Horror

description: Catbug assembles an away team to save the day, while the Warriors handle things on deck. Featuring friends old and new like, Impossibear, RoboChris, Halycon and Slippy Napkins who is voiced by Polly Livingston (voice of Tree Trunks from Adventure Time).
name: Catbug's Away Team

description: Chris and Plum play a little Merwif Tag and little does Chris know... it makes them trade bodies! Chris with clappy pig hands and Plum with swooshy hair, and what about movie night with Beth?!
name: Merewif Tag

description: The Bravest Children come across a potential brain sucker, growing in Ralph Waldo Pickle Chip's garden and causes Wallow to become highly suspicious. You can't fool his dolls! But this doesn't bode well... Wallow needs their help!!
name: The Dimension Garden

description: Chris is whisked away on a mission of great importance by an unseen force operating in the shadows. Oh wait, it's just the Emotion Lord. Chris discovers his ultimate mission to save his soul, and change his fate.
name: The Parasox Pub

description: In the first part of a two part finale, hamsters flee from the invisible hideout and the Bravest Warriors need to figure out what the heck is going on! Wallow receives a Falcon Mod, Danny steps it up and Beth kicks butt!
name: Season of the Worm

description: In the second part of the two part finale, Beth, Danny and Wallow face off against Ralph Waldo Pickle Chips and the Aeon Worm! How will they stop them from causing chaos? Watch to find out what happens!
name: Season of the Mitch

description:
Japanese title: Masukarēdo –Kamen Butōkai– (Masquerade –仮面舞踏会–)

Usagi has learned Princess D from the Kingdom of D, biggest resource-producing country of precious stones, will exhibit her legendary secret treasure. Suspecting it might be the "Legendary Silver Crystal", Usagi sneaks into the embassy of Kingdom of D.
name: Act 4 Masquerade Dance Party

description:
Japanese title: Makoto –Sērā Jupitā– (まこと –Sailor Jupiter–)

All of Juban Middle School is talking about the "cursed bridal shop", where every men who visits is said to disappear. Just then, a tall girl with superhuman strength, Makoto Kino, transfers to the school!
name: Act 5 Makoto - Sailor Jupiter -

description:
Japanese title: Takishīdo Kamen –Takishīdo Masuku– (タキシード仮面 –Tuxedo Mask–)

Tuxedo Mask has been reported to have committed many crimes to obtain the "Legendary Silver Crystal". Luna and others are convinced he's the enemy, but Usagi can't believe it…
name: Act 6 Tuxedo Mask

description:
Japanese title: Koi mo mata seishun no ichi buna no desu / Ai to wa futari de oroka ni naru koto desu (恋もまた青春の一部なのです / 愛とはふたりで愚かになることです)

Rock Lee has a crush on Sakura Haruno. He mounts numerous "love offenses" his target, but Sakura manages to easily brush them off. Later, Lee goes to slip a love letter into her shoebox, in hopes of getting closer to Sakura.
name: Love is a part of the Springtime of Youth / Love makes both sides Crazy

series.name: NARUTO Spin-Off: Rock Lee & His Ninja Pals

description:
Japanese title: Tensai ninja Neji to shōbuna no desu / Tenten ni wa yuzurenai tatakai ga aru no desu (天才忍者ネジと勝負なのです / テンテンには譲れない戦いがあるのです)

Lee's teammate Neji Hyuga is a talented ninja referred to by many as a genius. He is so talented that he took out an enemy boss from the Hidden Grass Village in one strike!
name: A Competition With the Genius Ninja, Neji/Tenten's Must-Win Battle

series.name: NARUTO Spin-Off: Rock Lee & His Ninja Pals

description:
Japanese title: Soredemo Gai Sensei wa yattenai…desu / Kakashi Sensei wa Gai Sensei no raibaru desu (それでもガイ先生はやってない…です / カカシ先生はガイ先生のライバルです)

Lee's beloved Guy Sensei is arrested for lewd behavior! Lee promises to clear his master’s name. Later, Kakashi Sensei's secret move defeats Guy, and Lee decides to follow Kakashi and become as powerful as he is.
name: Guy Sensei Didn't...Do It... / Guy Sensei's Rival Is Kakashi Sensei

series.name: NARUTO Spin-Off: Rock Lee & His Ninja Pals

description:
Japanese title: Konohamaru ni kenpō o oshieru no desu / Kenkōshinda wa shōbu pantsu de idomimasu (木ノ葉丸に拳法を教えるのです / 健康診断は勝負パンツで挑みます)

Konohamaru usually practices ninjutsu with Naruto. But now he's sought out Rock Lee to learn better hand-to-hand combat skills. Later, Lee and the others are ordered to undergo a routine physical exam.
name: I'm Going to Teach Konohamaru Kempo/ I Save My Lucky Undies for Physicals

series.name: NARUTO Spin-Off: Rock Lee & His Ninja Pals

description:
Japanese title: Konoha no sato no dai undōkai desu/ Gibasen wa seishun no daigomina no desu (木ノ葉の里の大運動会です／騎馬戦は青春の醍醐味なのです)

The Hidden Leaf Village is holding a sports meet! Lee is called to read the Athlete's Pledge of Fair Play, but screws up in front of the entire stadium. Hoping to save face, he swears to outperform everyone at every event.
name: The Leaf Village Sports Meet/ Calvary Battles Are Part of the Thrill of Youth

series.name: NARUTO Spin-Off: Rock Lee & His Ninja Pals

description:
Japanese title: Orochimaru wa Sasori-za B-gata desu! / Raburetā wa saidai no wanana no desu (大蛇丸はさそり座Ｂ型です！／ラブレターは最大の罠なのです)

Lee and his team are on guard duty at the front gate, but they'll have to be extra vigilant. Later, Lee is flummoxed by Guy-sensei's new "Smooth Operator Fist."
name: Orochimaru Is a B-Type Scorpio/ Love Letters Are the Ultimate Trap

series.name: NARUTO Spin-Off: Rock Lee & His Ninja Pals

description: Raven and Beast Boy are shocked to discover that their exes, Terra and Aqualad, are now dating each other.
name: Rocks and Water

description: Mordecai wants to share a piece of cake with C.J.
name: 1000th Chopper Flight Party

description: Meg gets a new job at the airport, where she's instantly popular for being the hottest employee there. Meanwhile, Cleveland becomes a therapist and starts giving Peter and Lois relationship advice, but Peter quickly becomes frustrated and threatens to tell Donna a big secret about what went down at Cleveland's bachelor party.
name: Dr. C & The Women

description:
Japanese title: Hokage datte hagerutoki wa hageruno desu! / Orochimaru wa tottemo shitsukoii otoko nano desu! (火影だってハゲるときはハゲるのです／大蛇丸はとってもしつこい男なのです)

Lee's team is pulling bodyguard duty for the Fifth Hokage Tsunade while she's off on a gambling binge. Later, Orochimaru summons Manda to swallow Tsunade, Naruto, and even Guy-sensei whole!
name: Even Hokage Wear Out / Orochimaru Is Persistent

series.name: NARUTO Spin-Off: Rock Lee & His Ninja Pals

description:
Japanese title: Hinata wa Neji no itokona no desu / Hinata no jakuten wa Naruto desu (ヒナタはネジのいとこなのです／ヒナタの弱点はナルトです)

Neji's cousin Hinata is trying to get some training in, but it's not easy with Lee constantly getting in the way. Later, Lee and several others don a familiar orange outfit.
name: Hinata Is Neji's Cousin / Hinata's Weak Point Is Naruto

series.name: NARUTO Spin-Off: Rock Lee & His Ninja Pals

description:
Japanese title: Chīmuwāku koso seishun no akashi desu / Han'nin wa kono naka ni iru! Desu! (チームワークこそ青春の証です／犯人はこの中にいる！です!)

After seeing Shikamaru and Choji in action, Lee attempts to strengthen his friendship with Neji. Later, the Leaf ninja are scheduled to take an IQ test, but on the way to the exam, Lee's team discovers Guy Sensei collapsed on the ground!
name: Teamwork Symbolizes Youth / the Culprit Is Among Us!

series.name: NARUTO Spin-Off: Rock Lee & His Ninja Pals

description:
Japanese title: 古都といえば、修学旅行です! / 女子の部屋と書いてお菓子箱です!

Lee and Naruto are both vying to be on Sakura's team for a research trip to the old capital city. Later, evening falls and Lee wants to slip away from all the Sensei to go hang out with the girls.
name: A Field Trip to the Old Capital! / Girls' Rooms and Candy Boxes

series.name: NARUTO Spin-Off: Rock Lee & His Ninja Pals

deck: Coulson and his team are still reeling from a shocking revelation that leaves the team fractured as they must decide what to do with one of their own. Meanwhile, Bobbi and Mack reveal their true allegiance to Hunter, while elsewhere, Ward and Agent 33 embark on a personal mission.
description:
Former S.H.I.E.L.D. Agent 33 and Agent Ward are living a life on the run without S.H.I.E.L.D. or HYDRA to protect them. They kidnap the inventor of the nanomask, who isn't able to remove it, but does fix it so it can store up to 3 faces at a time, or be turned off, revealing the facial scarring. The pair use the mask to enter a secure Air Force base and kidnap HYDRA agent Sunil Bakshi to get revenge.

Meanwhile, Mack takes Hunter to meet “the real S.H.I.E.L.D.”, another SHIELD cell formed after the HYDRA infiltration.
name: Love in the Time of Hydra

description: Christian and Deena hunt for Calista with help from Retro Girl while Johnny Royalle makes his return public.
name: Like A Power

deck: Leo is suspicious when Spike emerges leading a team called the Mighty Mutanimals; the Turtles must brave the bizarre world of Dimension X to save the enslaved people of New York.
name: Battle for New York, Part 1

deck: War comes to Coulson’s doorstep in a way he never anticipated as shocking revelations are brought to light, and Skye struggles to control her new abilities but will soon make a decision that irrevocably changes her life.
description:
Tasked with boarding the Hydra-infested aircraft carrier Illiad, to rescue commander Gonzales and sink the ship to prevent Hydra from getting it's secrets, Agents Bobbi Morse and Isabelle Hartley instead rescue engineer Mack, and Gonzalez and along with a few other, decide to take back the ship and reconstitute S.H.I.E.L.D. without the secrets that Nick Fury kept that they believe led to Hydra's success.

Morse steals the "Fury's toolbox" from Coulson's office. Meanwhile Simmons is tasked with both creating gloves to inhibit Skye's powers, as well as breaking into said toolbox for "the real S.H.I.E.L.D." agents who take over Coulson's base.
name: One Door Closes

description: Rick and his group face a number of challenges while trying to secure their new home.
name: Spend

deck: Chase tries to help Koda adapt to modern day technology after he struggles to learn how to ride their new high tech Dino Cycles. But when they are caged in a cave by one of Sledge's monsters, Koda must rely on his caveman instincts to escape and save his friend.
name: Return of the Caveman

deck: When a Maori fortune teller asks Chase for help guarding her shop from a potential thief, Chase is happy to help, but falls under the spell of Sledge's latest monster, Spellbinder. The rest of the Rangers must quickly figure out how to help break Spellbinder's hold on Chase before their friend is lost to them forever.
name: Breaking Black

deck: Leo is suspicious when Slash emerges leading a team called the Mighty Mutanimals; the Turtles must brave the bizarre world of Dimension X to save the enslaved people of New York.
name: Battle for New York, Part 2

deck: Norma and Norman focus on Annika's disappearance; Norma learns the truth about the Arcanum Club.
name: The Arcanum Club

deck: Norman and Emma make decisions regarding their future; Norma informs Norman of his boundaries.
name: A Death in the Family

description: The Ghost Crew make a final desperate attempt to rescue Kanan from the Empire.
name: Fire Across the Galaxy

description: Triphammer is developing a way to surprises powers and Castlia is forced to choose where she stands.
name: Mickey Rooney Cries No More

has_staff_review.name: Powers Episode #103: "Mickey Rooney Cries No More"

description: DIGGLE MARRIES LYLA; THE SUICIDE SQUAD RIDES AGAIN - It's celebration time as Diggle (David Ramsey) and Lyla (guest star Audrey Marie Anderson) get married. However, Deadshot (guest star Michael Rowe) interrupts their honeymoon and tells them the Suicide Squad has been given a new mission - rescue United States Senator Joseph Cray (guest star Steven Culp) from a hostage situation in the Republic of Kasnia. Amanda Waller (guest star Cynthia Addai-Robinson) breaks down the mission and introduces them to the newest member of the Suicide Squad, Cupid (guest star Amy Gumenick). Meanwhile, Oliver (Stephen Amell) learns about Ray's new Atom costume and the two have a heated stand-off. Felicity (Emily Bett Rickards) and Ray hit a rough patch.
name: Suicidal Tendencies
The Great Secret of The Universe
Bring Me The Head of Earthworm Jim
